title: Rangers take lead on bizarre play in Game 5 of ALDS
text:
> Texas Rangers take lead on bizarre play in Game 5 of ALDS Texas Rangers' Rougned Odor, left, celebrates with Prince Fielder after scoring a run during the seventh inning in Game 5 of baseball's American League Division Series against the Toronto Blue Jays, Wednesday, Oct. 14, 2015 in Toronto. (Nathan Denette/The Canadian Press via AP) MANDATORY CREDIT
